sub_title: Student International Master's in Central European, Eastern European, Russian and Eurasian Studies. Available for (temporary) work.
summary:
Student International Master's in Central European, Eastern European, Russian and Eurasian Studies (IMCEERES). Open to job offers.

Successfully finished first year of IMCEERES. Because of COVID I temporarily paused my master's studies, as I intended to do a semester in Russia, but because of the volatile COVID situation I decided to postpone my second year until 2022. Therefore, I am now open to (temporary) job offers, preferably with one or more of the following ingredients:
► International Relations
► Russia, Russian, Eastern Europe
► Political Economy


► Organisations dealing with policy making, sustainability, social awareness, international development
►Part time
► Situated in the Amsterdam or The Hague area
